snippet.title: ForeVR Darts Teaser Trailer - Coming Soon to Oculus Quest & Quest 2! Play with Hands or Controllers!
snippet.description:
Coming soon: https://forevr.la/darts 
Win a copy of ForeVR Darts: https://forevr.la/windarts

Supported Platforms: Quest, Quest 2
Developer: Forevr Games Inc
Website: http://forevrgames.com/

Experience Oculus’ latest Hand Tracking technology in the perfect game to play with your hands: Darts! 

Stock your arsenal with a selection of 50+ uniquely weighted darts with custom effects and attributes, featuring a range of classic designs and fantastical flights. Explore 3 immersive Darts halls and choose from 1000s of songs on the YouTube powered jukebox or stay tuned in to each hall’s curated playlist. Get competitive with Double Out (501, 301) in public multiplayer or keep it casual with 501, 301, 201, and 101 modes in Single Player, Pass-and-Play, or a Private room with friends. Create or join public or private multiplayer rooms to face off against players all around the world. Create private multiplayer rooms to play versus friends and family online or use Pass-and-Play to play with one headset locally. Prefer to play solo? Challenge in-game pro NPCs to hone your skills and level up.

ForeVR Darts gets players’ hands on VR like no other sports game can!
